CC Wire Analyzer is released under a split license depending on the type of
content:

• Source code (`.py`, `.spec`, `.js`, `.html`, `.css`, `.yml`, build scripts,
  etc.) — **MIT License** (below).
• Documentation and prose (`README.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, files
  under `docs/`, and the prose content of in-app text) —
  **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)**.
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Bundled third-party assets retain their own licenses (see the notice at the
bottom) and are not covered by the MIT or CC BY 4.0 grant above.

